column5: A friend of mine is starting a You Tube channel, have a look at the link above. Makes me look at the snow outside and cry  Have a good morning everybody.  MTBF
Great video! Very well made! Consider me subscribed.
Theirs not a better experience fishing then catching a musky while casting.  Trolling will get you more, but for the battle and experience its always nicer with casting.
Why didn't I think of that?? Using deer as a topwater bait for Musky.  Seriously though, great video.
just goes to show you how important doing your L turns and figure 8's are. Good video. I can speak from experience that it is not easy using those big nets by yourself !
